'''Ayman Zakaria jomaa''' ({{lang-ar|ايمن زكريا جمعة}}) is a Lebanese [[Brand]] and [[Marketing strategy|Marketing Strategist]] who partners with [[CEO]]s, executives as a consultant for personal and professional brands, human-to-human. He was graduated from [[American University of Beirut]] on 2002 by holding a B.S degree on [[Computer engineering|computer]] & [[Telecommunications engineering|communication engineering]]. After spending nearly 9 years working in various positions and experience at [[telecommunication|telecom]], [[Value-added service|VAS services]], [[TerraNet AB|Terra net]] and Business Development Manager at [[Libancall]], he has landed coverage in providing platforms and services with respect to telecom solution that led to a private firm named DoubleU group which is an [[Value-added service|VAS services]] that providing environment in telecom services and content marketing context while it's activities spread in [[Middle East]] and [[North Africa]](MENA) with more than 112 million subscriber.<ref>[http://www.telecomreview.info/index.php/articles/interviews/615-l-intelligence-artificielle-est-l-avenir-par-le-pdg-du-groupe-numbase « L’intelligence artificielle est l’avenir », par le PDG du Groupe Numbase]</ref><ref>[http://www.teknotel.info/index.php/features/telecom-industry/871-ayman-gomaa-digital-transformation-and-artificial-intelligence-are-the-future بيان توضيحي من المهندس ايمن زكريا جمعة]</ref><ref>[https://www.eliktisad.com/news/show/261474/%D8%A3%D9%8A%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%AC%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%A9:-%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%B2%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A5%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%86-%D8%A3%D9%86%D9%87-%D9%8A%D9%85%D9%84%D9%83-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%81%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A7%D9%85 أيمن جمعة: يوم يزعم الإنسان أنه يملك المعرفة الكاملة يعني أنه انتهى]</ref><ref>[https://cccl.org.lb/News-Details/24/n/449/Cash-In-New-Service-in-Support-of-CCCL Cash In New Service in Support of CCCL]</ref> He is also known as co-founder of Muzeit corporate1 and Numbase Group2 which offers platforms and services on mobile technology.<ref>[https://www.elnashra.com/news/show/984953/%D8%B4%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%83%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8A%D8%AC%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A8%D9%8A%D9%86-TVShout-%D9%88%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA-Numbase-Group شراكة استراتيجية بين TVShout وشركات Numbase Group]</ref>
